<br>
But let's just say for example, some mage from uberguild X were to come here and say:<br>
<br>
&quot;Hey Hey, I've got uberitem AAA, yes I know 99% of you scum can't get that, but you have to know how uber I am now, worship me, and yes that means spell X is better than spell Y for me now, so all do what I say scum, I'm the benchmark for you to bow down before!&quot;<br>
<br>
... it should not take a world genius to figure out how us 'scum' are going to react.<br>
